<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>SwiftUI on 编程心语</title><link>https://www.ithome.me/tags/swiftui/</link><description>Recent content in SwiftUI on 编程心语</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 23 Jul 2026 08:00:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.ithome.me/tags/swiftui/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>SwiftUI @MainActor 深入理解：告别主线程崩溃与 UI 无响应</title><link>https://www.ithome.me/post/2026/07/23/swiftui-mainactor-deep-dive/</link><pubDate>Thu, 23 Jul 2026 08:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.ithome.me/post/2026/07/23/swiftui-mainactor-deep-dive/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="为什么你的-swiftui-应用偶尔白屏或崩溃"&gt;为什么你的 SwiftUI 应用偶尔白屏或崩溃？&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;如果你写过 SwiftUI 应用，大概率遇到过这种场景：App 跑起来后点几下按钮，界面突然卡住不动，或者控制台冒出一堆 &lt;code&gt;Main Thread Checker&lt;/code&gt; 警告，甚至直接崩溃。常见的错误信息是：&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>用SwiftUI打造懂鸟App：iOS原生观鸟助手完整开发指南</title><link>https://www.ithome.me/post/2026/06/15/%E7%94%A8swiftui%E6%89%93%E9%80%A0%E6%87%82%E9%B8%9Fappios%E5%8E%9F%E7%94%9F%E8%A7%82%E9%B8%9F%E5%8A%A9%E6%89%8B%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97/</link><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jun 2026 08:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.ithome.me/post/2026/06/15/%E7%94%A8swiftui%E6%89%93%E9%80%A0%E6%87%82%E9%B8%9Fappios%E5%8E%9F%E7%94%9F%E8%A7%82%E9%B8%9F%E5%8A%A9%E6%89%8B%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="为什么选swiftui原生"&gt;为什么选SwiftUI原生？&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;iOS原生开发在这类项目上有天然优势：&lt;/p&gt;
